description:
Very nice rooms with hot showers, air conditioning and fan, also good wifi ; 
the breakfast is very rich;
relaxation area with hammock;
Very good value for money

Big parking area with lots of shadows. 
During the day they try to charge but is public. During the night no one is here to charge. Beach front and nice quiet place.  
Good spot! 

